<H3> <TI>   Montenegro's Djukanovic Arrives in London for Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Montenegro's Djukanovic Arrives in London for Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1406115494 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1020 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1406115494 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] <LOCATION>London</LOCATION>, 14 Jun (TANJUG)--A delegation of the 
Republic of <LOCATION>Montenegro</LOCATION> headed by Prime Minister <PERSON>Milo Djukanovic</PERSON> 
arrived in <LOCATION>London</LOCATION> today. British Foreign Secretary <PERSON>Douglas Hurd</PERSON> 
will receive the delegation this afternoon. 
  Tomorrow at the British parliament, the Montenegrin prime 
minister will meet the members of the British-Yugoslav 
parliamentary group who arranged the invitation to the 
Montenegrin delegation. 
  Deputy Prime <PERSON>Krunoslav Vukcevic</PERSON> and Foreign Minister <PERSON>Miodrag 
Lekic</PERSON> also arrived in <LOCATION>London</LOCATION>. 

</TEXT>

