  [Excerpts] <LOCATION>Podgorica</LOCATION>, 16 Jun (TANJUG) -- Industrial output 
in <LOCATION>Montenegro</LOCATION> dropped by almost <PERCENT>21 percent</PERCENT> in <DATE>May</DATE> compared with 
<DATE>April</DATE>, the republic's statistics institute has disclosed. 
[passage omitted] 
  According to the figures released, prices in <LOCATION>Montenegro</LOCATION> were 
