<H3> <TI>   Montenegrin Economy Termed `Hopeless' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94P20505A Ljubljana GOSPODARSKI DNEVNIK in Slovene 3 Mar 94 
p 28 </F>

<F P=103> 94P20505A </F>
